criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          1. Age:40-80;

          2. BMI < 30kg/m2；

          3. ASA classification:Ⅰ-Ⅲ；

          4. Undergoing elective laparoscopic gastrectomy.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          1. Preoperative history of inflammatory intestinal diseases, intestinal flora disorders,
             obstructive jaundice, intestinal obstruction, irritable bowel syndrome and other
             digestive diseases;

          2. Severe heart, lung, liver, kidney, brain and other diseases;

          3. Serious infection, pancreatitis, burns, trauma, need a large dose, long-term use of
             antibiotics before the operation;

          4. A history of abdominal surgery;

          5. Combined with gravis myasthenia, serious electrolyte disorders or neuromuscular
             diseases.
